when the robber pounced from the nearby sand dunes.He fled with their backpack, which contained a camera,
their identity documents, and other valuable goods.Klaus said that their assailant was aggressive and did
not say anything when he attacked them.They were found by a woman who was walking her dogs.The couple had been in Mzansi for three months, having
